        <abstract>
            <p>Thanks QdeB for his continued support of CD’s election to French Academy.</p>
            <p>Discusses views of Milne-Edwards on species.</p>
            <p>Comments on views of Élie de Beaumont.</p> 
<p>"I fear my next book [<hi rend="italic">Descent</hi>] … will greatly displease you."</p> 
        </abstract>
